{
  "stem": "21786.7",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now we were there to clean after bombardments, for the Allied knew about the camp and they successfully always bombed it in time so that it did-- wasn't producing too much.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So if somebody was an engineer, was carrying probably iron rods or bags of cement or architects.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so slowly, there were only about 20 people left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We were workers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when they asked me what I'm-- my profession of work, so I said I'm a laundryman.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They ask me where did I pick up the kind of a trade like laundryman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And so I named the company, Racek-- R-A-C-E-K-- in Prague, which really existed, which I remembered only.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that was all.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was thinking, simply, if you are in the camp and you want to stay inside, you don't want to do anything with these huge buildings here.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You have to do something which is needed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now cook, many people would pretend that they are cooks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some kind of a tailor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Really, they-- they could ask you, I mean, to do something as a tailor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I thought it was the laundry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Laundry has to be washed from time to time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I picked up as a laundryman.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to make the story very short, I was given a commando, which varied between 10 people up to 120 people, depending on how much laundry was to be done in the main factory.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't wash our laundry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only we washed the laundry for the civilian workers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was-- it was good for three days a week.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a relatively soft job in comparison as anything else.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
